#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
bool possible( int n)
{
    int sum=0;
    while(n)
    {
        sum+=n%10;
        n/=10;
    }
    if(sum<=1)
        return false;
    else
        return true;
}
int main()
{
    int test, n;
    cin>>test;
    while(test--)
    {
        cin>>n;
        if(possible(n))
            cout<<"YES"<<endl;
        else
            cout<<"NO"<<endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
